  "detailed_description": "<strong>The doctor said today was my last appointment, I'm healthy. Time to go home, what could go wrong?</strong><br><br><strong>My Last Appointment</strong> is a short walking simulator inspired by liminal spaces, internet memes about backrooms and the aesthetics of the unpleasant corridors of post-Soviet medical facilities. This game will test your attention to details.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785980/extras/687f2357687e1854506da28af07221aa.poster.avif?t=1764658752\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785980/extras/687f2357687e1854506da28af07221aa.webm?t=1764658752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785980/extras/687f2357687e1854506da28af07221aa.mp4?t=1764658752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Approximate playthrough time is 15-60 minutes.</strong>",
